829
01:17:39,940 --> 01:17:41,720
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa?</font>

830
01:17:43,890 --> 01:17:50,170
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku menjadi sangat tersiksa karena Geumganggo.</font>

831
01:17:50,170 --> 01:17:55,620
<font color=#FFFF00>Tapi, kau tahu apa?
